repos.title: mobile-home-pricing-api
repos.description: his API provides up-to-date pricing information for mobile homes across various states, allowing users to fetch data on market trends, historical prices, and price predictions.

repos.title: real-estate-market-dashboard-api
repos.description: A Vue.js powered API for dynamic and interactive real estate market dashboards, focusing on mobile home parks. It integrates real-time data visualization of market values, demographic shifts, and investment opportunities.

repos.title: mobile-home-sales-insights-api
repos.description: A Nuxt.js based API for mobile home sales that provides insights into sales data, market saturation, and demand forecasts. Ideal for enhancing e-commerce platforms with server-side rendered content for improved user engagement and SEO.

repos.title: property-investment-api
repos.description: This API offers tools for analyzing investment opportunities in mobile home parks. It features capabilities for ROI calculations, market comparison, and financial modeling.

repos.title: mobile-home-valuation-engine
repos.description: An ElasticSearch implemented API tailored to quickly assess and provide valuation of mobile homes based on current market data, previous transactions, and regional economic indicators.
